  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates that while resiniferatoxin (RTX) can reduce some effects of cross-sensitization, it may also enhance somatic responses, limiting its therapeutic potential.",
    "The study uses an animal model of colonic inflammation to investigate cross-organ sensitization mechanisms.",
    "TRPV1 receptors show differential expression patterns in bladder versus colon during inflammation."
